": 37, "content": "- 全文件重写 → 用 write_file", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 38, "content": "- 搜索文件内容 → 用 grep", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 39, "content": "- 找文件路径 → 用 glob", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 40, "content": "- 批量替换所有相同字符串 → 用 replace_all", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 41, "content": "- old_block 不是原文片段，而是自然语言描述", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 42, "content": "", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 43, "content": "输入：", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 44, "content": "  path       要修改的文件路径，相对 workspace 或绝对路径", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 45, "content": "  old_block  要替换的原文块，必须来自文件原文，并且精确唯一匹配", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 46, "content": "  new_block  替换后的新文本块", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 47, "content": "", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 48, "content": "输出：", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 49, "content": "  ok            是否修改成功", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 50, "content": "  code          结果码", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 51, "content": "  path          修改文件路径", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 52, "content": "  replacements  替换次数，成功时固定为 1", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 53, "content": "  candidate     精确匹配失败但归一化后找到候选时返回，包含 original_block", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 54, "content": "", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 55, "content": "结果码：", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 56, "content": "  PATCH_APPLIED            修改成功", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 57, "content": "  OLD_BLOCK_NOT_FOUND      old_block 未找到，应重新 read_file 获取原文", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 58, "content": "  OLD_BLOCK_NOT_UNIQUE     old_block 出现多次，应扩大上下文后重试", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 59, "content": "  FUZZY_MATCH_ONLY         归一化后找到唯一候选，但未修改；应使用 candidate.original_block 重新调用", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 60, "content": "  FUZZY_MATCH_NOT_UNIQUE   归一化后找到多个候选，应读取更大上下文后重试", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 61, "content": "  WRITE_FAILED             写入失败", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 62, "content": "", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 63, "content": "重要规则：", "kind": "context"}, {"line": 64, "content": "- 不要编造 old_block；ol